the future and make it ours said clinton 
hes oldfashioned all right hes the kind of man who plays 
it straight keeps his word and pays his bills 
clinton 41 met dukakis in 1981 when he was teaching at the 
kennedy school and i was the youngest exgovernor in american 
history 
both of us were given a rare second chance by our people 
that does wonders for your sensitivity to others he said 
he has also been a soldier a lawyer a teacher a legislator 
he has excelled in all these roles because of his fine mind and his 
