atmospheric administration are asking for comment as required by 
law on their proposal to reject a plan first contemplated in 1959 
to eventually adopt the international standard of 03048 of a meter 
to define the foot 
instead the agencies propose to continue indefinitely use of 
the us survey foot which is defined as 12003937ths of a 
meter 
thats less than a millionth of an inch longer 
announcement of the proposal which becomes official only after 
anyone affected has a chance to comment was in the tuesday edition 
of the federal register 
