here is a transcript of the speech by rep daniel 
rostenkowski of illinois nominating sen lloyd bentsen of texas for 
vice president at the democratic national convention on thursday 
night 
i come before you tonight to nominate my friend and legislative 
partner sen lloyd bentsen to our partys nominee for vice 
president of the united states 
lloyd bentsen has everything it takes to become one of americas 
great vice presidents and michael dukakis has chosen the best 
teammate that america has to offer 
ive spent a lot of time with lloyd bentsen ive seen one 
victory after another earlier this year we enacted the greatest 
expansion of medicare ever 
later this year well finish a welfare reform bill the new 
trade bill will soon become law and were fighting to keep the tax 
system fair 
you dont negotiate through many nights under enormous pressure 
without taking the true measure of a man lloyd bentsen is 
straightforward lloyd bentsen is smart and yes lloyd bentsen is 
tough 
he knows that compromise keeps the political process running 
the victories havent come easily but through lloyd bentsens 
leadership important victories have been won and the nation is 
better for it 
lloyd bentsen is a member of the united states senate and i am 
a member of the house of representatives hes from texas and im 
from illinois 
we each have our own style but when you strip away our regional 
loyalties we both have the same goals for america 
i represent thousands of people on the northwest side of the 
city of chicago my constituents are people who run our stores 
work in our factories teach our children drive our buses and 
protect our neighborhoods 
but theyre lloyd bentsens constituents too 
they may not be famous one by one but together theyre the 
backbone of america and the soul of the democratic party 
they work hard theyre honest they pay their mortgages and 
taxes on time they live from paycheck to paycheck trying to put a 
little bit aside each month 
lloyd bentsen knows these people and has fought for these people 
thats why i want to make a special appeal to them tonight 
come home come home to your party come home to the party that 
has contributed so much to our social progress 
the democratic party is the party of your parents come home to 
the democratic party come on home where you belong 
we still believe that those who can work should have a good job 
that pays a decent wage that government should not turn its back 
on those who cant make it on their own that we can find our ways 
to educate our kids to fight drugs and crime to care 
compassionately for our elderly and to accomplish all this without 
breaking the bank 
lloyd bentsen believes that no one should get a free ride but 
no one should be left behind either 
isnt that what we all believe 
lloyd bentsen is one of a few men in public life who is at home 
with those who are trying to make it in america and those who 
already have he speaks the language of businessmen because he used 
to be one 
and he knows what business owes working americans 
thats why lloyd bentsen resisted republican efforts to gut 
social programs that we all depend on like protecting children and 
older americans like improving the lives of americas workers he 
fights for those who seek a better life because he knows they 
deserve it 
thats what our democratic party is all about 
and thats what lloyd bentsen stands for 
and that ladies and gentlemen is what this election is all 
about 
my fellow delegates in this hall my fellow democrats across 
this great country to all america it is a high honor and a great 
privilege to place in nomination as our candidate to be the next 
vice president of the united states the senior senator from the 
great state of texas lloyd bentsen 
