government have consficated over eight tons of cocaine paste in 
one year duran said 
bolivian police assisted by the dea destroyed two large 
cocaineprocessing laboratories in the beni region wednesday but 
officials did not say whether the labs belonged to suarez gomez or 
another trafficker 
dea spokesman jack hook said in miami that suarez gomez was 
indicted there in 1980 for conspiracy to peddle 854 pounds of 
cocaine but that suarez gomez commonly deals in tons of cocaine 
hes really the same as the upper levels of the medellin 
cartel said hook he could be considered one of the pioneers 
involved in growing manufacturing and trafficking cocaine to the 
united states 
hook noted that medellin cartel leader carlos lehder rivas was 
sentenced in jacksonville fla on wednesday to life in prison 
without parole 
last month the lower house of bolivias congress accused 
cocaine kingpins of trying to take over the government and called 
for a united front to preserve democracy 
the government in june closed a radio station and a television 
station that broadcast a talk show with suarez gomez on the show 
suarez gomez described the us state department as the king of 
cocaine the vice royalty is the government of bolivia and the 
