socalled night stalker case 
tynan pointed out ramirez a pale shaggyhaired drifter dressed 
in a loosefitting doublebreasted dark blue suit wih a blue 
hankerchief in his pocket to match his tie ramirez did not 
acknowledge the jury prospects and continued to sit with his back 
to them at the counsel table 
